<div id="review_3082864979" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3082864979" />
    <a title="Omar Delawar" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/53689026-omar-delawar"><img alt="Omar Delawar" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1631679373p2/53689026.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3082864979?book_show_action=true">Dec 16, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Omar Delawar" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Omar Delawar" href="/user/show/53689026-omar-delawar">Omar Delawar</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780340922651" href="/book/show/308257.Donnie_Brasco">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3082864979" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8284318555979420184">6 Year Undercover commitment from an FBI Agent to bring down the Italian Mob. He is still married after all that jazz. Imagine that. This is a short-read and I would get the audiobook version otherwise you are missing out on the audio-taped conversations between the wise-guys, mafia captains and Joe. Loved the narration as well - appropriately New York-Italian. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

